thread.title: Wayne & Sarah
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by Wayne & Sarah

author: Wayne & Sarah
title: Wayne & Sarah
text: The service we got from the staff was impeccable, but the car we got was disappointing. When I booked online, I had a choice of Kia or Hyundai, booked a Hyundai i20 purposely because I have had bad experiences with Kia's. When we picked up our car it was a Kia. We were heading up the Sunshine Coast and spending time in Montville and Flaxton. Needless to say the Kia fell short getting up the hills in that area!!!
